==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Commissionnaire
<hw>Com*mis`sion*naire"</hw> <pr>(?; F. ?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[F., fr. L. <ets>commissio</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>An agent
or factor; a commission merchant.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One of a class of attendants, in some European
cities, who perform miscellaneous services for travelers.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Commissionship</ent>⟦br⟧
